45
00:16:21,365 --> 00:16:23,164
Okay.

46
00:16:26,968 --> 00:16:30,505
Don't run off, though.
Be a shame to shoot you.

47
00:16:30,671 --> 00:16:33,575
Comrade junior lieutenant,
have you got some paper?

48
00:16:33,741 --> 00:16:35,875
Only your diary, but that's evidence.

49
00:16:36,609 --> 00:16:40,379
It's all about you and your friend...

50
00:16:40,547 --> 00:16:44,284
...and your anti-Soviet plotting.

51
00:16:44,549 --> 00:16:50,154
If I had my way,
