all the German you know.

86
00:39:03,436 --> 00:39:07,606
Don't worry,
the war's over for me.

87
00:39:09,708 --> 00:39:13,310
I'll get the chain off and go home.

88
00:39:14,177 --> 00:39:18,181
Do you understand?

89
