will burn out and leave the chimney.

220
00:53:12,445 --> 00:53:13,913
A chimney.

221
00:53:35,764 --> 00:53:40,968
We'll boiI or fry them,
then eat them.

222
00:53:41,135 --> 00:53:44,037
You want to go
to the other world?

223
00:53:44,205 --> 00:53:50,443
Drink the broth of toadstooIs.
Those will just make you sick.

224
00:53:50,610 --> 00:53:53,979
Can't be bothered?
Don't. It's easy.

225
00:53:54,146 --> 00:53:58,716
Don't worry!
I'll cook them.

226
00:53:58,883 --> 00:54:03,053
The sergeant in my battalion
