that taking a life...

240
00:55:20,584 --> 00:55:23,888
...Iengthens their own.

241
00:55:24,055 --> 00:55:26,824
Put the barreI back afterwards.

242
00:55:43,271 --> 00:55:46,207
Ma'am, I need saIt.

243
00:55:46,373 --> 00:55:51,277
I'm not mad enough
to eat mushrooms!

244
00:55:51,444 --> 00:55:53,913
I see. In the house.

245
00:57:08,976 --> 00:57:11,643
Scum!

246
00:57:13,045 --> 00:57:16,416
The water brought a Ietter.

247
00:57:19,384 --> 00:57:24,455
